OL,3,CMore than a third support ban on
OL,4,Cgreyhound racing in Wales
OL,6,FMore than a third of people support
OL,7,Fthe idea of banning greyhound racing
OL,8,Fin Wales, according to the results of
OL,9,Fa Welsh Government consultation.
OL,11,FOf nearly 740 individual responses,
OL,12,F36.37% were in favour of introducing a
OL,13,Fphased ban, compared to 25.12% against
OL,14,Fit.
OL,16,FNearly three-quarters also agreed that
OL,17,Fa licensing scheme should be
OL,18,Fintroduced in Wales to strengthen
OL,19,Fexisting legislation around activities
OL,20,Flike greyhound racing.
