OL,6,FThe consultation did not contain a
OL,7,Frecommendation as to whether a
OL,8,Fpotential ban would be considered.
OL,9,FThis was met with disappointment by
OL,10,Fdog and animal charities, describing
OL,11,Fdog deaths or injuries "in the name of
OL,12,Fentertainment" as "unacceptable".
