OL,3,CMore than a third support ban on
OL,4,Cgreyhound racing in Wales
OL,6,FHowever the Greyhound Racing Board of
OL,7,FGreat Britain (GBGB), who regulate the
OL,8,Findustry, welcomed the consultation
OL,9,Fpublication. The board acknowledged
OL,10,Fthe "clear support for licensing" and
OL,11,Fwas pleased by "the opportunity for
OL,12,Fcontinued engagement and collaboration
OL,13,Fon ways to optimise the welfare of
OL,14,Fracing greyhounds".
OL,16,FWales is home to one greyhound racing
OL,17,Ftrack, Valley Stadium, in Ystrad
OL,18,FMynach - which is regulated by the
OL,19,FGBGB.
