OL,7,Fits next steps in Spring 2025.
OL,9,FThe consultation, which looked into
OL,10,Fthe licensing of animal welfare
OL,11,Festablishments and activities, ran
OL,12,Fbetween December 2023 and March this
OL,13,Fyear, garnering 1,180 responses.
