OL,6,FThose in support of the ban cited
OL,7,Freasons of animal welfare and a belief
OL,8,Fthat the industry is "unethical". Key
OL,9,Fissues included injuries to animals,
OL,10,Foverbreeding, inadequate legislation
OL,11,Fand a desire to prevent unnecessary
OL,12,Fsuffering and deaths.
