OL,6,FRespondents on the other side of the
OL,7,Fargument said a ban would have a
OL,8,Fnegative economic and cultural impact.
OL,9,FMany suggested further regulation and
OL,10,Flicensing could address welfare
OL,11,Fconcerns instead and some feared that
OL,12,Fthis would also set a precedent for
OL,13,Fbanning other animal sports, like
OL,14,Fhorse racing and dog agility.
OL,16,FAnother question asked for views on
OL,17,Fwhether a licensing scheme should be
OL,18,Fintroduced to strengthen existing
OL,19,Flegislation regarding animal exhibits.
OL,20,FThere were 719 responses to this
OL,21,Fquestion, which revealed:
