OL,6,FA number of responses suggested
OL,7,Flicensing would raise standards and
OL,8,Fencourage accountability. A high
OL,9,Fnumber of the responses in support
OL,10,Falso favoured a ban on animal exhibits.
OL,12,FOf those who answered no, some said
OL,13,Fthey would prefer an outright ban
OL,14,Fwhile others said current legislation
OL,15,Fwas sufficient enough. Some
OL,16,Frespondents raised concern over the
OL,17,Ffinancial cost and burden of new
OL,18,Fregulation too.
