OL,6,FMore than half of respondents to
OL,7,Fanother question also supported
OL,8,Flicenses for individual owners and/or
OL,9,Fkeepers or trainers of racing dogs,
OL,10,Fwhile 40% were against the idea.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government has not yet
OL,13,Fannounced how it will move forward
OL,14,Ffrom the results of the consultation.
