OL,4,Cgreyhound racing in Wales
OL,6,FThe Cut the Chase Coalition, which
OL,7,Fconsists of Dogs Trust, RSPCA Cymru,
OL,8,FBlue Cross, Greyhound Rescue Wales and
OL,9,FHope Rescue, said it was disappointed
OL,10,Fthat the government has not taken "the
OL,11,Fsteps needed to end the completely
OL,12,Favoidable deaths of hundreds of dogs
OL,13,Feach year by bringing greyhound racing
OL,14,Fto an end in Wales".
OL,16,FA similar decision was recently taken
OL,17,Fin New Zealand, where greyhound racing
OL,18,Fwill now be outlawed by the end of
OL,19,FAugust 2026.
