OL,6,FSpeaking on behalf of the Cut the
OL,7,FChase Coalition, Owen Sharp, Chief
OL,8,FExecutive of Dogs Trust, said: "The
OL,9,Fcall to end greyhound racing in Wales
OL,10,Fhas received overwhelming support from
OL,11,Fthe animal welfare community, Members
OL,12,Fof the Senedd, and the public, with
OL,13,Fover 35,000 people signing a petition
OL,14,Fdemanding change.
