OL,3,CMore than a third support ban on
OL,4,Cgreyhound racing in Wales
OL,6,F"It is unacceptable that so many dogs
OL,7,Fdie or are seriously injured every
OL,8,Fyear, all in the name of
OL,9,Fentertainment. Wales now stands
OL,10,Falongside only a handful of countries,
OL,11,Fincluding England and Scotland, where
OL,12,Fthis outdated and inhumane practice
OL,13,Fpersists.
OL,15,F"The Welsh Government must take the
OL,16,Fonly meaningful action to stop this
OL,17,Fcruelty: end greyhound racing once and
OL,18,Ffor all."
