OL,6,FHowever The GBGB said the responses
OL,7,Fdemonstrated clear support for
OL,8,Flicensing and an emphasis on a
OL,9,F"measured response", that acknowledges
OL,10,F"the positive economic, social,
OL,11,Fcultural and welfare impact GBGB
OL,12,Fregulation has had on the sport in
